data.description: Spacious Georgetown Township home, this private retreat sits on a wooded acre with its own small pond, creating a seamless blend of nature and luxury on a very private lot, with no Association (HOA). With 6 bedrooms and 4-1/2 bathrooms, including a main floor master with an ensuite bathroom and a cozy reading nook, this home offers comfort and convenience. The main floor boasts a well-equipped kitchen with a snack bar and dining area, alongside a convenient main floor laundry. The living room's two-story ceilings add to the open and airy atmosphere, overlooked by the extra sitting area on the second floor. Upstairs, you'll find four additional bedrooms and two full bathrooms, plus the sitting area, providing ample space for various uses. The lower level offers versatility with a large rec/game area, additional living room space, a sixth bedroom and full bath, a bar area, and abundant storage space. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with a brand-new furnace, A/C, humidifier and air purification system all with a 10 year transferrable warranty! Plus updated flooring through much of the home. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Schedule your showing today and experience the perfect harmony of natural beauty and comfortable living in this Georgetown Township home.
